28:46.159 --> 28:47.516
You -- You --

28:47.518 --> 28:49.751
You knew about Janine.

28:49.753 --> 28:52.846
Uh, about me and her?
You knew this whole time?

28:52.848 --> 28:54.398
Mm-hmm.

28:55.944 --> 28:57.735
It's just, you know,
I -- I --

28:57.737 --> 29:01.005
